lead_paragraph: The Sacramento Kings beat the Raptors on Sunday in a controversial finish that left Toronto coach Dwayne Casey struggling to accept the outcome.

headline.print_headline: Bizarre Finish Has Raptors Crying Foul After Loss to Kings
